{
  "verses": [
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ir tee Praueecht aisees\npa Webjam / jo tas (Deewa)\nWahrds ne irr pee winneem/pa-\nscheem teem tas ta notiks.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tapehz fatka tas KUNGS\ntas Deews Zebaot: Tapehz ka\njuhs scho Wahrdu fakkat: Rau-\ngt/es darritchu mannu Wahrdu\njuhsu Mutte par Ugguni/ un\nfchohs Landis par Malku/ un\ntas winnas aprihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Redsi / es atweddischu\npahr jums weenn Tautu no tah-\nkenes/ tu Israëta Nams/ fatka\ntas KUNGS: Ta irr weena\nstipra Tauta/ weena wezza Tau-\nta/ weena Tauta/ ka Wallohu\ntu ne faprohti/ un ne nomanni/\nfo ta runna.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Winnas Bułebu-Maks\nirr ka atwehrts Kaps/ tee irr wis-\nfi Nebehonceki.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un ta ehdihz tawu Pkau-\njumu/ un tawu Matsi/ kas ta-\nweem Dehleem / un tawahm\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Meitahm bij ja-ehd/ ta ehdihz\ntawas Arvis/ un tawus Wehr-\nschus/ ta ehdihz tawu Wihna-\nKohku/ un tawu Wihges-Kohku/\ntawus stiprus Pilsfahtus/ uhs\nfo tu połanjees/ darrihs tee zaur\nSohbinn nabbagus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tomehr es ir tannis\nDeenäs ne gribbu wiſat ar\njums Gallu darriht/ fatka tas\nKUNGS.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Un kad juhs fazziteet:\nRapehz irr tas KUNGS muhsu\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Deews muhs wiffas schahs Lee-\ntas darrijs? Tad buhs tew uhs\nwinneem fazziht: Itt ka juhs\nmanni effat atstahjutchi / un\nfwescheem Deetweem juhāSem-\nmē kalpojschi / tapatt kalpojeet\njuhs Swescheem weena Semmē\nkas jums ne peederr.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Sluddinajeet to Jehlaba\nNamnā/ laischat no ta eeksch\nJuhda dsirdeht/ un jakkajt:\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Klausajt jelle scho juhs\ngelkigi un nefamannigi Lau-\ndis/ kam Azzis irr/ un ne reds/\nkam Aufis irr/ un ne dsird.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne gribbat juhs manni\nbihtees? fatka tas KUNGS:\nNe gribbat juhs manna Preek-\nschā drebbeht? kas es tahs Smil-\ntis tai Juhrai par Rohbeschu lee-\nku ar weenu mubschigu Lifku-\nnu/ ka tai pahr to ne buhs pahr-\neet/ jepschu winnas Wilxi kns-\ntahs/ tad tee tomehr ne eespehs/\njepschu tee gann kanz/ tad tee to-\nmehr pahr to ne pahrees.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Bet scheein Laudim iru\natkahpaja un pahrgalwiga\nSirđs/ tee atkahpj/ un aiseet\nnohst.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 24,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Un ne fatka sawā Sirđi:\nLaid mehs jelle to KUNGU\nmuhsu Deewu bihstamees/ kas\nmums Leetus dohd agri un wehsi\nsawa Laikā/ kas mums tahs no-\nliktas Meddetas ta ptauama\nLaika pasarga.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 25,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Juhtu Noseegumi no-\ngreesch schibs Leetas/ un juhsu\nP 2\nGreb-\n"
    }
  ],
  "confidence": "high",
  "notes": ""
}
